36
00:02:15,743 --> 00:02:20,066
[SPEAKER_06]: We have budget transfers, journal entry 20850 for $5,169.06, journal entry 20851 for $275 and journal entry 20852 for $800.

37
00:02:20,106 --> 00:02:26,231
