00:37:42,584 --> 00:37:48,349
[SPEAKER_06]: And if you have more questions, here's how you navigate the handbook kind of scenario.

447
00:37:49,830 --> 00:38:10,155
[SPEAKER_06]: because the handbook is really, I mean, to say that people read it before they sign off on it at the beginning of the year is like we're all kidding ourselves, but the handbook is there and so the most important thing is that you know it's there and you can go find it if you have a question, which is good, but are there some salient things that would be useful for people to know right up front?

