00:39:05,460 --> 00:39:08,524
[SPEAKER_10]: I also think we should revisit the notion of people signing off.

457
00:39:08,684 --> 00:39:14,710
[SPEAKER_10]: We're literally asking everybody to sign and say they did something that very few families have done.

458
00:39:14,730 --> 00:39:16,873
[SPEAKER_10]: And that just feels a little icky.

