680
00:59:50,290 --> 01:00:06,876
[SPEAKER_18]: But what we had decided and what we have reflected in this is to really look at what it would be to have that range, what would it be to have an auditorium that has 500 seats, 750 seats, which is the cap for MSBA, 800 seats, and 1,000 seats.

